channel.title: (No Silabs) Solution-X V1 317 Amazingly Stable(FIRST SERVER RELEASE W00T)
channel.description:
Credits: Testscape (base) Killamess-Tuts Bakatool- Tuts
This is going to be the new *Delta* of 317 servers! A lot more stable and way more compatible, clean, and organized.
This is my very first server, so please give me a break. I found Testscape source from google search. I just wanted to say sorry also because I didn't have enough time to take more pictures. I will be adding more later. Here are some
features:
Prayer-100% Combat-100% Herblore-80% Slayer-15% (Removing Chest Exp, and adding monster exp) Mining-90% Smithing-90% Range-100% Mage-100% RuneCrafting-75-80% Firemaking-100% (Walk West when fire lights) Woodcutting-100% Cooking-50% (all cooking fish/meates work 100% cooking bread, cakes, pies 0%) Health-100% Agility-80% Thieving-90% (Stalls work 100%, but havent added pickpocketing to all NPC's yet) Crafting- 100% (gems only) Fletching-100% (Bows/arrows) Fishing-75% (only works in some areas) Farming-25% (Needs a lot of work)
New home, starter, exp gain, pickup server (only for v1), duel arena 100%, Adding more shops, adding my own custom gs mini (V2), adding dungeoneering type minigame (V2) and so much more!
[u][i][b]DOWNLOAD[/b][/i][/u]: http://uppit.com/v/4ZA2R2C5
